Package model.portfolio

Interface BetterPortfolio

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Portfolio
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BetterPortfolioImpl
    public interface BetterPortfolio
extends Portfolio
    An interface for the betterPortfolio. This interface implements new methods that a better portfolio requires.

      • plot

        java.lang.String plot​(java.time.LocalDate from,
                      java.time.LocalDate to)
               throws java.lang.IllegalArgumentException
        Returns the plot of the portfolio from the given date to the given date. The plot of the portfolio is returned as a string, where the string is a bar graph of the value of the portfolio over time. The bar graph should be generated by the FormattingUtils class.
        Parameters:
        from - the date to start the plot from.
        to - the date to end the plot at.
        Returns:
        the graph of the portfolio from the first given date to the last given date.
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if either date is null.
